					Quốc hội qua các nhiệm kỳ
			</a>
  </div>
  
 <div style="float: left;">
              <img title='Photo: , License: N/A' height='101' alt='12232.jpg' width='140' class='teaser-image' src='/polopoly_fs/1.297282.1306013716!/image/2266801495.jpg_gen/derivatives/box_w140/2266801495.jpg' />
